    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><i><strong>“如果你真要离开这个寒冷的世界，我希望是为了更绿的草原，而不是空中的雪花。”</strong></i></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >以你的沉着蔑视整个世界</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3149680/extras/44a04038d16b32867a7af96f9bd47522.poster.avif?t=1758336045\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3149680/extras/44a04038d16b32867a7af96f9bd47522.webm?t=1758336045\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3149680/extras/44a04038d16b32867a7af96f9bd47522.mp4?t=1758336045\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >化解永无止境的怪物屠戮。攻占中立营地并征用它们的力量来助力你的祈愿。勇敢直面苔原泰坦的挑战。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >夺取圣坛并守卫战略要点</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3149680/extras/611c477064faa00760a8755935c23535.poster.avif?t=1758336045\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3149680/extras/611c477064faa00760a8755935c23535.webm?t=1758336045\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3149680/extras/611c477064faa00760a8755935c23535.mp4?t=1758336045\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >控制圣坛以获得令人惊叹的增益。保卫圣坛免遭精英怪物攻击以守护你的新能力。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >在Maple和Aluna之间切换</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3149680/extras/fb6026f2432ea2d874b99f4f493f1816.poster.avif?t=1758336045\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3149680/extras/fb6026f2432ea2d874b99f4f493f1816.webm?t=1758336045\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3149680/extras/fb6026f2432ea2d874b99f4f493f1816.mp4?t=1758336045\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >化身Aluna从远处瞄准，或作为Maple近身交战。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >借助强大的奥术强化自身</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3149680/extras/961c4814609d8dec6a47d38b7670d2d3.poster.avif?t=1758336045\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3149680/extras/961c4814609d8dec6a47d38b7670d2d3.webm?t=1758336045\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3149680/extras/961c4814609d8dec6a47d38b7670d2d3.mp4?t=1758336045\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在你的配装中打造专门强项以应对任何形势。在每一轮冒险中适应进化，从而尽可能长久地生存下去。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >继承前辈的重托</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >跨越这片寒冬废土，结识新面孔并缅怀那些曾经与你并肩作战的挚友。</p>",
